                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]
    UNION ALL
        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1], 
        [Limit2].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
        [Limit2].[Id1] AS [Id], 
        [Limit2].[Id2] AS [Id1], 
        [Limit2].[MonthRent] AS [MonthRent],

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent12] ON [Extent11].[CommunityId] = [Extent12].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project3]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project3].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]

        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1],

    [Project2].[Name1] AS [Name1], 
    [Project2].[CreateDateTime1] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Name] AS [Name], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
        [Limit1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum],

        [Limit1].[CityId] AS [CityId],

        [Limit1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime],

        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

    [Project2].[Name] AS [Name], 
    [Project2].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
    [Project2].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt],

    [Project2].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
    [Project2].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project2].[Id1] AS [Id1], 
    [Project2].[Name1] AS [Name1], 
    [Project2].[CreateDateTime1] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Name] AS [Name], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
        [Limit1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
        [Limit1].[Email] AS [Email], 
        [Limit1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
        [Limit1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
        [Limit1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
        [Limit1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

    [Project2].[CreateDateTime1] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id],

        [Limit1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt],

        [Limit1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

    [Project2].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
    [Project2].[Email] AS [Email], 
    [Project2].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
    [Project2].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
    [Project2].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
    [Project2].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project2].[Id1] AS [Id1], 
    [Project2].[Name1] AS [Name1], 
    [Project2].[CreateDateTime1] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Limit1].[Id] AS [Id], 
        [Limit1].[Name] AS [Name], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
        [Limit1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
        [Limit1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
        [Limit1].[Email] AS [Email], 
        [Limit1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
        [Limit1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
        [Limit1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
        [Limit1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]
    UNION ALL
        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1], 
        [Limit2].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
        [Limit2].[Id1] AS [Id], 
        [Limit2].[Id2] AS [Id1], 
        [Limit2].[MonthRent] AS [MonthRent],

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]

    [UnionAll1].[IconName] AS [C65], 
    [UnionAll1].[CreateDateTime9] AS [C66],

    [UnionAll1].[C7] AS [C73]
    FROM  (SELECT 
        CASE WHEN ([Join8].[AttachmentId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1],

                [Filter1].[Id8] AS [Id],

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]
    UNION ALL
        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1], 
        [Limit2].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime],

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent11]

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project3]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project3].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_HousePics] AS [Extent19] ON [Limit2].[Id] = [Extent19].[HouseId]) AS [UnionAll1]
    ORDER BY [UnionAll1].[CreateDateTime] DESC, [UnionAll1].[Id] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id1] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id2] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id3] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id4] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id5] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id6] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id7] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id8] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id9] ASC, [UnionAll1].[C1] ASC

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]
    UNION ALL
        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1],

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project3]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project3].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]

            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Extent1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]

            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent12] ON [Extent11].[CommunityId] = [Extent12].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Extent11].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent11].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit2]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_HousePics] AS [Extent19] ON [Limit2].[Id] = [Extent19].[HouseId]) AS [UnionAll1]
    ORDER BY [UnionAll1].[Id] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id1] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id2] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id3] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id4] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id5] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id6] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id7] ASC, [UnionAll1].[C1] ASC

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]

        CAST(NULL AS bit) AS [C7]

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]

        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1],

[Extent17].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime21], [Extent17].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted21]
                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent11]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent12] ON [Extent11].[CommunityId] = [Extent12].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project3]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project3].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_HousePics] AS [Extent19] ON [Limit2].[Id] = [Extent19].[HouseId]) AS [UnionAll1]
    ORDER BY [UnionAll1].[CreateDateTime] DESC, [UnionAll1].[Id] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id1] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id2] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id3] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id4] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id5] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id6] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id7] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id8] ASC, [UnionAll1].[Id9] ASC, [UnionAll1].[C1] ASC

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)

                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent11]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent12] ON [Extent11].[CommunityId] = [Extent12].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent16] ON [Extent11].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent16].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent18] ON [Filter3].[TypeId] = [Extent18].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter3].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter3].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project3]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project3].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]

                    FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent1]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[CommunityId] = [Extent2].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[RegionId] = [Extent3].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent3].[CityId] = [Extent4].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent5].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent1].[RoomTypeId] = [Extent6].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent7] ON [Extent1].[StatusId] = [Extent7].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent8] ON [Filter1].[TypeId] = [Extent8].[Id]
                WHERE ([Filter1].[CityId] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Filter1].[TypeId] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
            ORDER BY row_number() OVER (ORDER BY [Project1].[CreateDateTime] DESC)
            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent9].[AttachmentId] AS [AttachmentId], [Extent9].[HouseId] AS [HouseId], [Extent10].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent10].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent10].[IconName] AS [IconName], [Extent10].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent10].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_HouseAttachments] AS [Extent9]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Attachments] AS [Extent10] ON [Extent10].[Id] = [Extent9].[AttachmentId] ) AS [Join8] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join8].[HouseId]

        SELECT 
        2 AS [C1],

        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

    [Project2].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
    [Project2].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt],

    [Project2].[Name1] AS [Name1], 
    [Project2].[CreateDateTime1] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
    [Project2].[IsDeleted1] AS [IsDeleted1]

        [Limit1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted], 
        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes], 
            [Extent1].[LastErrorDateTime] AS [LastErrorDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

        [Join1].[Id] AS [Id1], 
        [Join1].[Name] AS [Name1], 
        [Join1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime1], 
        [Join1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Join1].[AdminUserId] IS NULL) THEN CAST(NULL AS int) ELSE 1 END AS [C1]
        FROM   (SELECT TOP (2) 
            [Extent1].[Id] AS [Id], 
            [Extent1].[Name] AS [Name], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordHash] AS [PasswordHash], 
            [Extent1].[PasswordSalt] AS [PasswordSalt], 
            [Extent1].[PhoneNum] AS [PhoneNum], 
            [Extent1].[Email] AS [Email], 
            [Extent1].[CityId] AS [CityId], 
            [Extent1].[LoginErrorTimes] AS [LoginErrorTimes],

            [Extent1].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], 
            [Extent1].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM [dbo].[T_AdminUsers] AS [Extent1]
            WHERE (0 = [Extent1].[IsDeleted]) AND ([Extent1].[Id] = @p__linq__0) ) AS [Limit1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN  (SELECT [Extent2].[AdminUserId] AS [AdminUserId], [Extent3].[Id] AS [Id], [Extent3].[Name] AS [Name], [Extent3].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime], [Extent3].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted]
            FROM  [dbo].[T_AdminUserRoles] AS [Extent2]
            INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Roles] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent3].[Id] = [Extent2].[RoleId] ) AS [Join1] ON [Limit1].[Id] = [Join1].[AdminUserId]
    )  AS [Project2]
    ORDER BY [Project2].[Id] ASC, [Project2].[C1] ASC

[Extent14].[CreateDateTime] AS [CreateDateTime18], [Extent14].[IsDeleted] AS [IsDeleted18], [Extent15].[Id] AS [Id19], [Extent15].[TypeName] AS [TypeName7], [Extent15].[Name] AS [Name16],                     FROM       [dbo].[T_Houses] AS [Extent11]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Communities] AS [Extent12] ON [Extent11].[CommunityId] = [Extent12].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Regions] AS [Extent13] ON [Extent12].[RegionId] = [Extent13].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_Cities] AS [Extent14] ON [Extent13].[CityId] = [Extent14].[Id]
                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent15] ON [Extent11].[DecorateStatusId] = [Extent15].[Id]

                    INNER JOIN [dbo].[T_IdNames] AS [Extent17] ON [Extent11].[StatusId] = [Extent17].[Id]
                    WHERE 0 = [Extent11].[IsDeleted] ) AS [Filter3]

            OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 10 ROWS ONLY  ) AS [Limit2]
